Briefcase
=========

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/briefcase.svg
   :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/briefcase
   :alt: Python Versions

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/briefcase.svg
